name: YABG! - Yet Another Ball Game
tagline: YABG! is Yet Another Ball Game smillar to HaxBall
body:
# Welcome on YABG! project page
YABG! (Yet Another Ball Game is ball game smillar to HaxBall but in full 3d

## Feature plan for 1.0 version:
* Multiplayer for 2-10 players
* Basic gameplay smillar to soccer or american football
* One or more gamemodes
* 1 -5 stadiums

More info comeing soon...
